definition: to transmit/to lead/to guide/to conduct/to direct
thread/string/wire/line/CL:條|条[tiao2],股[gu3],根[gen1]/(after a number) tier (unofficial ranking of a Chinese city)

sentences.english: These ignition wires send the charge to each spark plug.
sentences.chinese: 这些点火导线将电荷运送至每个火花塞。

sentences.english: The coil is a wound conductive wire having a cross-section of rectangular-shape.
sentences.chinese: 线圈是通过卷绕截面为扁平形状的导线而得到的。

sentences.english: He is hitting the wire leader with his spear, he thought.
sentences.chinese: 它正用它的长嘴撞击着铁丝导线，他想。

sentences.english: With a cell and a wire, can you make two bulbs light up?
sentences.chinese: 仅用一根导线和一节电池能让两个小灯泡亮起来吗？

sentences.english: Unlabelled terminals must not be used as "tie points" for other wires.
sentences.chinese: 不可将无标号的接线端当成其它导线的“结点”。

sentences.english: Electrical contact is made with the leaf springs by in each case one of the conductor tracks.
sentences.chinese: 板簧各与至少一个印制导线电触点接通。

sentences.english: Just make sure to hide the wires, lest mess up the illusion.
sentences.chinese: 不过一定要把导线藏好，否则就露馅了。

sentences.english: The traverse net is one of the main method of seting up horizontal control nets.
sentences.chinese: 导线网是建立平面控制网的主要方法之一。

sentences.english: Gears whine as turrets traverse, zeroing in on the lead elements.
sentences.chinese: 齿轮哀炮塔作为导线，在零对铅元素。

sentences.english: The two ends of the wire are connected to a split-ring commutator.
sentences.chinese: 导线的两端联接到裂环整流器。

sentences.english: With wires of the thermostat contacts short sub commissioning, heating normal.
sentences.chinese: 用导线将温控器的触点短接试机，制热正常。

sentences.english: Unplug the antenna coaxial cable connector from the radio chassis.
sentences.chinese: 从收音机底盘拔开天线同轴导线。

sentences.english: Now let's get the energy for the line.
sentences.chinese: 现在我们来推导线的能量。

sentences.english: When this happens it’s best to get clamps to stick the wires to the walls.
sentences.chinese: 这种情况下你最好把导线钳到墙上去。

sentences.english: This shrinking permits the wire to activate a pump that atomizes a volatile substance.
sentences.chinese: 这种导线的收缩驱动一个泵以雾状喷出挥发物质。

sentences.english: This allows other data traffic on the 1-Wire bus during the conversion time.
sentences.chinese: 在转换时间，这允许在1导线公共汽车的其他数据量。
